U||   white, but more agitated, was the face of the defendant’s counsel, who
U||   instantly rose.
U||   “For some unexplained reason, your Honor, my client desires to suspend
U||   further proceedings, with a view to effect a peaceable compromise with
U||   the plaintiff. As he is a man of wealth and position, he is able and
U||   willing to pay liberally for that privilege. While I, as his counsel,
