U||   help he was to me in studying the part, and for the bad humor he was in
U||   about it. He refused to let me, so I did it anyhow. I could easily
U||   spare the three hundred.
U||   Sincerely yours,
U||   H. Hopkins Hargraves.
U||   P.S. How did I play Uncle Mose?
U||   Major Talbot, passing through the hall, saw Miss Lydia’s door open and
U||   stopped.
U||   “Any mail for us this morning, Lydia, dear?” he asked.
U||   Miss Lydia slid the letter beneath a fold of her dress.
U||   “The Mobile Chronicle came,” she said promptly. “It’s on the table in
U||   your study.”
