U||   voice.
U||   “Atrocious!” she exclaimed. “Atrocious! Simply atrocious, Belmont. This
U||   is a house of public entertainment. They can’t turn us out in this
U||   high-minded manner! Isn’t there a law or something to that effect?”
U||   “It wouldn’t matter if there was,” he thoughtfully replied. “This
